ej.microui.event.controller

Class DispatchEventHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • ej.microui.event.controller.DispatchEventHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ButtonEventHandler, CommandEventHandler, EventGeneratorsHandler, PointerEventHandler, EventHandler

    public class DispatchEventHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventHandler, EventGeneratorsHandler, ButtonEventHandler, CommandEventHandler, PointerEventHandler
    Dispatches events by event type (defined Event) and data (event type specific).
    Since:
    2.0
